milestones.description: Tim de Leede and Jeroen Smits's 30-run partnership is NED's highest for the 10th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 23 between Lefebvre and Adeel Raja
Lefebvre has broken the record for most ODIs (5) as captain for NED, going past Lubbers
This is the lowest match aggregate (286) involving teams England & Netherlands in ODIs
Tim de Leede has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (9) for NED, going past Bas Zuiderent
Tim de Leede has become the top scorer for NED in ODIs with 203 runs, going past Klaas-Jan van Noortwijk's 168
